Body:
Thereupon [a voice] called out to her from beneath that
			[palm-tree]:<span class='fn'>18</span> "Grieve not! Thy Sustainer has provided a
			rivulet [running] beneath thee;

And after he had withdrawn from them and I from all that they
			were worshipping instead of God, We bestowed upon him Isaac and
			Jacob, and made of them a prophet;
